components.name: Campaign Item
components.description: This component is used within the Campaigns Loop.

components.name: Campaigns
components.description: This component contains a Campaigns Pattern that loops through all of the Campaign entries from Contentful. Each Campaign Item is displayed dynamically per Member in the frontend.

components.name: Container
components.description: This component should be included within every Composition. It can be contained on the page with left and right margins or be displayed as full width.

components.name: Header
components.description: This component represents the Member Dashboard header.

components.name: Eligibility Form
components.description: The component displays the eligibility form.

components.name: Fitness Locations
components.description: This component displays the top three fitness locations based on the Member's zip code.

components.name: Grid
components.description: This component holds Grid Items and provides control of up to twelve grid columns.

parameters.name: Is this the SilverSneakers Go Hero?
parameters.helpText: Checking this parameter will display the App Store & Google Play images in place of the primary and secondary buttons.

components.name: Link Card
components.description: This is a card component that includes an internal CTA link.

components.name: Link Card Grid
components.description: This is a grid component that holds 2, 3, or 4 Link Cards.

components.name: Live Classes
components.description: This component displays the top three "LIVE" or "Up Next" online classes from the "/live" api endpoint.

components.name: Member Dashboard
components.description: This is a wrapper component that has a Member Dashboard Pattern which contains all of the Member Dashboard components.

components.name: Member Profile
components.description: This is a wrapper component that holds all of the Member Profile components.
